lead_paragraph: Twice major winner Zach Johnson has built a career record that most of his peers would envy but it gnaws at him that he has yet to taste Ryder Cup success after playing for the United States on four teams.

headline.print_headline: Ryder Cup Success Still Eludes Johnson's Docket
